atan.parser

Interface CommandFilter


  • public interface CommandFilter
    An interface that shall help to filter the different server commands (see, hear, error, ...). Implementaions of this interface are used as parameter for the parser which will call the appropreate methods. As probably not all messages from the server will have to be completely parsed the command filter acts as a preselection of commands.
